=Description=

With this project we pretend to criate a movement of the project: Meet your Neighbor, where the idea is the empowerment of the neighbors of the building or condominium to realize their colective dreams, starting maping theirs super powers. And the call is: What is your super power? What do you really like to do?
Examples: Cooking, gardening, music, painting, hand craft, languages, drawing, crochê, reciclyng, ...


